{"tid":1208360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本台外判司機混亂中受傷　頭部流血一度失去知覺送院","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T09:21:25.000Z","uid":37554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"34e5f94ff488584281f4ec0fc84d0e149c9b14c5","tid":1208360,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"2019-06-12 HKT 17:03<br />\n大批反對修訂《逃犯條例》的市民繼續在金鐘政府總部及立法會一帶聚集，警員多次向示威者投擲催淚彈，又曾經發射布袋彈及橡膠彈，迫使示威者向中環方向後退，本台有外判司機受傷，送到瑪麗醫院救治，據了解他送院時一度失去知覺，頭部流血。<br />\n<br />\n另外，消息指，有多名在今次衝突事件中的傷者，送往瑪麗醫院救治。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462378-20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462378-20190612.htm&d=LMVY6Z7nIekaHefcscWgVdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=88bd0ba3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462378-20190612.htm&h=eb5d474e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462378-20190612.htm</a>"}]}